metadata.name: Raven #1
metadata.description:
Raven is a powerful figure who transforms the world from loss, to prophecy, to insight. Raven connects the material world with the world of spirits beyond. Raven is a collection of original, generative, poetry, music and art. 

The music and poetry were composed by Emil, recorded at Salt Spring Studios and performed by Emil G Music.

Stable Diffusion, trained by SpaDogs, was used locally in the studio, to create the art for this project.  

The end result, ethically produced, original poetry, music and art.

Side note: Vinyl records were played in the studio while the neural network did its thing.  

What’s not to love?

Quadraphonic is encoded using Involve Encode™ Surround Stereo down-mix & universal stereo audio format.
